lead_paragraph: Celtic's hopes of a claiming a domestic treble this season were dashed when they suffered a 3-1 defeat by Ross County in the League Cup semi-final at Hampden Park on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Ross County End 10-Man Celtic's Treble Dream
